	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sure, $08 is fine. $7F is insurance against NES clones (including inaccurate emulators).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

